https://www.zabbix.com/download

Select the agent OS and other information for installation instruction and follow them.
https://www.zabbix.com/download?zabbix=7.0&os_distribution=rocky_linux&os_version=9&components=agent_2&db=&ws=

# rpm -Uvh https://repo.zabbix.com/zabbix/7.0/rocky/9/x86_64/zabbix-release-7.0-4.el9.noarch.rpm
# dnf clean all
b. Install Zabbix agent2
# dnf install zabbix-agent2 zabbix-agent2-plugin-*
c. Start Zabbix agent2 process
Start Zabbix agent2 process and make it start at system boot.

# systemctl restart zabbix-agent2
# systemctl enable zabbix-agent2
